Quick question - do you have any interesting stories about the sunsetting of a favorite product? Specifically those who have done it in a nice way?
Trapit - one of our main clients - moved away from customer focus to b2b
CEO announced it in a very cut to the chase blog post
which was not met with great enthusiasm from the people who'd helped them get there
Hank, product owner, wrote a much more in depth/honest post about the rationale for why they're moving
not a great or deep story, but one that showed both sides of a sunsetting
Here's Hank's post: <http://blog.trap.it/blog/bid/362387/An-Important-Announcement-on-the-Evolution-of-Trapit>
